This is a solid Ranked Team expecting to make plat+ with ease and we are looking to consolidate our roster with finding good, active players for both the main roster and reserves (reserves will play very often too).

Requirements:
Plat+ Solo queue rank (or with a valid reason why you aren&#039;t such as you just transferred servers)
Must be very active in the upcoming weeks.
Verbal communication in the form of Skype.

Currently the roles available for tryout are Jg, Mid, Support.

If you wish to try out please either add me in game or reply to this post in the following format (and I will add you in game).

In game name: &lt;&lt;Your In game Name&gt;&gt;
Role(s): &lt;&lt;Your Role&gt;&gt;
Current Rank: &lt;&lt;Your Current Rank&gt;&gt;
Top 3 Champions In Role(s) (no order required): &lt;&lt;Champion,Champion,Champion&gt;&gt;
